## Frontend environment variables (Vite)
## Copy to .env.local (recommended) or .env
##
## Base URL for the PHP API (no trailing slash)
## If running: `php -S localhost:8000 -t backend`
## then API_BASE is: http://localhost:8000/api
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

##
## Backend (PHP) — copy variables above into backend/.env as needed, or use backend/.env.example.
## FRONTEND_ORIGIN must match how you open the app in the browser (scheme + host + port), e.g.:
##   FRONTEND_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
## Multiple dev URLs: FRONTEND_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173,http://127.0.0.1:5173
## Unset or * = allow any origin (dev only).

